---
title: "US22 — View community posts"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>SocialScreen (Community)
  participant C as «Control»<br/>LoadFeed
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Post
  A->>B: open Social tab
  B->>C: load()
  C->>E: listFeed()
  alt posts found
    E-->>C: Post list (workout_share, level_up, challenge_result)
    C-->>B: state = AsyncData (feed models)
    B-->>A: scrollable community feed
  else empty
    E-->>C: empty list
    C-->>B: state = AsyncData (empty)
    B-->>A: "No posts yet"
  end
  note over E: listFeed via SocialGateway → posts (RLS) [planned]
